<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Gracias | XRed</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap');

    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #121212, #1f1f1f, #ff4b2b);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(31, 31, 31, 0.85);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 75, 43, 0.8);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ff4b2b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      animation: glow 2.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ddd;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    .signature {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #ff7043;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #ff4b2b;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 75, 43, 0.6);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #e03e1d;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(224, 62, 29, 0.8);
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      from {
        text-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff4b2b, 0 0 12px #ff7043, 0 0 20px #ff4b2b;
      }
      to {
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff4b2b, 0 0 30px #ff7043, 0 0 40px #ff4b2b;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 12px 30px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>¡Gracias por confiar pi en XRed!</h1>
    <p>Tu apoyo nos impulsa a crear moda que trasciende. Esperamos que cada prenda te haga sentir único y auténtico.</p>
    <p class="signature">— El equipo XRed</p>
    <a href="https://xred.com" target="_blank" class="btn">Visita nuestra tienda</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
